title: Fran Drescher Enters Whining
description:
Fran Drescher is the absolute king of taking a not necessarily average voice and making it iconic, she enters whining but leaves swimming in cash. This week Ashley and Claire comb through her life from Queens to Los Angeles and literally every vacation in between. 

Episode starts at 7:35

Thanks, Dame. Get 10% off your first order at dameproducts.com - promo code worm.

Get 20% storewide at bollandbranch.com promo code WORM at checkout.


We’re coming to Chicago!! Get tickets for our show at The Lincoln Lodge May 14!


We’re doing another live digital show with Momenthouse! This time it’s for the Australian-ish time zone on April 27, get tickets here!


Join the Patreon for new episodes every Thursday! This week we’re talking about The Ultimatum and more!
